{"tid":1304308,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"油塘要人啊！！！！！！！！！！！！！！","createTime":"2019-07-10T14:42:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T15:02:31.000Z","uid":162866,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c36c38aa831a6f52f61819db191924837b6655fb","tid":1304308,"uid":162866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:42:09.000Z","msg":"大家食飽飯落來幫手啊啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59df5646f842b663ca5b97670f30c4d012f73c2a","tid":1304308,"uid":162866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:43:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a1f71f59b04cda0959e4c40ba51a53e3ea92b8c","tid":1304308,"uid":265972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c36c38aa831a6f52f61819db191924837b6655fb","tid":1304308,"uid":162866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:42:09.000Z","msg":"大家食飽飯落來幫手啊啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:44:06.000Z","msg":"俾廢老搞事時，如果佢地出手打人，係咪可以合力制服佢地， 一路拍片一路大聲講行使緊市民拘捕權<br />\n<br />\n《刑事訴訟程序條例》第一○一（二）條，任何人可毋須手令而逮捕任何他合理地懷疑犯了「可逮捕罪行」的人。不過，市民若要行使拘捕權，須遵守一些限制。<br />\n<br />\n        限制一：只可向觸犯了「可逮捕罪行」的人行使。按《釋義及通則條例》第三條，「可逮捕罪行」（arrestableoffence）是指法庭可判處超過十二個月監禁的罪行，例如強姦、非禮、盜竊、搶劫等。即是輕微罪行例如扔棄垃圾，便不是可逮捕罪行，大家無權拘捕垃圾蟲。<br />\n<br />\n        限制二：在行使拘捕時不可使用過份武力，在當時環境而言屬於合理的武力。<br />\n<br />\n        限制三：市民必須將被拘捕者交警員，在合理範圍內盡快將該人帶給裁判官依法處理。<br />\n<br />\n        例如，在「陳鎮坤案」（HCMA63/2012）中，超市女員工拘捕涉嫌非禮她的顧客。她當時不准被告離開，又在被告要逃走時追趕及捉住他，然後報案。法庭裁定該員工所用的武力合理，其拘捕合法。案中的小插曲是，裁判官竟然錯誤地認為「非禮」及「普通襲擊」均是可逮捕罪行。上訴庭指出，「普通襲擊」並不是可逮捕罪行，因為其最高判刑只是十二個月監禁。<br />\n<br />\n        一般人遇上罪案，可能難以分辨當時情況是否可以行使市民拘捕權。故此，大家在見義勇為拘捕了罪犯後，應該盡快交由警方處理，方為上策。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.h1.com.hk/dailynews/headline_news_detail_columnist.asp?id=309147&sect;ion_name=wtt&amp;kw=50\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.h1.com.hk%2Fdailynews%2Fheadline_news_detail_columnist.asp%3Fid%3D309147%C2%A7ion_name%3Dwtt%26kw%3D50&d=RGEj3L6UPYZQbhamDwVV3Q%2BoCD4UrwaevtQIqI6x5z0%3D&h=c0cdad7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.h1.com.hk/dailynews/headline_news_detail_columnist.asp?id=309147&sect;ion_name=wtt&amp;kw=50</a>"},{"pid":"5c0c511851ff61446c849915b083424499cc745e","tid":1304308,"uid":156341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:02:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}